- Download and install https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=42637
- Go to `C:\Program Files (x86)\Reference Assemblies\Microsoft\Framework\.NETFramework`. Most likely, there will now be a folder named `v4.5.2`, but not a folder named `v4.5`.
- Make a copy of the `v4.5.2` folder, and rename the copied folder to `v4.5`.
- Done.
